----- DISASSEMBLED -----
.class public .class/MyClass
.super java/lang/Object

.class_end
----- INPUT -----
; Tests that a directive token can be used as package name.
; This should produce an error because .class is a directive, not an identifier.
; Expected: parser error about unexpected token

.class public MyClass
.super java/lang/Object
.package .class

.class_end
